### ===================================================
### Episode endpoints
### ===================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

### Login first (needed for auth)
# @name loginRequest
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin"
}

### ---------------------------------------------------
### CRUD
### ---------------------------------------------------

### Create episode
###
### NOTES 
### - Use `OFFP`/`OFFE` prefixed IDs so the outbox triggers the full
###   A28 + A01 sequential flow; central will assign the real PID/enctid.
### - `{{$randomInt 100000 999999}}` keeps IDs unique between runs so reposts
###   don't collide with previous test data.
# @name createEpisode
POST {{baseUrl}}/episodes
Authorization: Bearer {{loginRequest.response.body.access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mrn": "OFFP{{$randomInt 100000 999999}}",
  "num_episodio": "OFFE{{$randomInt 100000 999999}}",
  "paciente": "Pacient prueba {{$localDatetime iso8601}}",
  "sexo": "M",
  "fecha_nacimiento": "1985-04-12T00:00:00",
  "tipo": "Ambulatorio",
  "ubicacion": "Consulta Telemedicina",
  "estado": "Activo",
  "motivo_consulta": "Dolor abdominal",
  "data_json": {
    "Paciente": "Pacient prueba {{$localDatetime iso8601}}"
  }
}

### List all episodes
GET {{baseUrl}}/episodes
Authorization: Bearer {{loginRequest.response.body.access_token}}

### List episodes filtered by type
GET {{baseUrl}}/episodes?type=Ambulatorio&skip=0&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{loginRequest.response.body.access_token}}

### Get episode by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/episodes/{{createEpisode.response.body.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{loginRequest.response.body.access_token}}

### Update episode
### Use a `ubicacion` that exists in central (CTLOC) — the previous example
### `Piso 3` would be rejected on the next sync.
PUT {{baseUrl}}/episodes/{{createEpisode.response.body.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{loginRequest.response.body.access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "estado": "Alta",
  "ubicacion": "Consulta Telemedicina"
}

### Delete episode
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/episodes/{{createEpisode.response.body.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{loginRequest.response.body.access_token}}

### ---------------------------------------------------
### Patient delete (ADT^A29) — closes the patient lifecycle
### ---------------------------------------------------
###
### Deletes the patient (person) record AND all of their local episodes.
### For each synced episode an ADT^A23 is enqueued; for the patient itself
### an ADT^A29 is enqueued. Local-only IDs (OFFP*/OFFE*) are removed
### without notifying central.
###
### Typical close-out flow:
###   1. createEpisode  → A28 + A01 (sync assigns real PID/enctid)
###   2. POST a clinical note (optional) → ORU^R01
###   3. PUT episode (e.g. estado=Alta) → A08
###   4. DELETE patient by MRN → A23 (per episode) + A29 (person)
###
### Use the MRN returned by createEpisode AFTER it has been synced with
### central (it will no longer start with OFFP).

### Step A — Re-fetch the episode to get the (post-sync) real MRN
# @name fetchForDelete
GET {{baseUrl}}/episodes/{{createEpisode.response.body.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{loginRequest.response.body.access_token}}

### Step B — Delete the patient by real MRN
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/patients/{{fetchForDelete.response.body.mrn}}
Authorization: Bearer {{loginRequest.response.body.access_token}}

### Step C — Trigger upstream sync so A23/A29 are sent to central
POST {{baseUrl}}/sync/trigger
Authorization: Bearer {{loginRequest.response.body.access_token}}

### Step D — Verify the episode no longer exists locally
GET {{baseUrl}}/episodes/{{createEpisode.response.body.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{loginRequest.response.body.access_token}}

### ---------------------------------------------------
### Unique values
### ---------------------------------------------------

### Get unique episode types
GET {{baseUrl}}/episodes/types/unique
Authorization: Bearer {{loginRequest.response.body.access_token}}

### Get unique locations
GET {{baseUrl}}/episodes/locations/unique
Authorization: Bearer {{loginRequest.response.body.access_token}}

### Get unique locations filtered by type
GET {{baseUrl}}/episodes/locations/unique?tipo=Ambulatorio
Authorization: Bearer {{loginRequest.response.body.access_token}}
